00:57:50.600 --> 00:57:51.980 align:middle line:90%
And so you find--

00:57:51.980 --> 00:58:03.460 align:middle line:90%


00:58:03.460 --> 00:58:05.063 align:middle line:90%
And then you have --

00:58:05.063 --> 00:58:10.900 align:middle line:90%


00:58:10.900 --> 00:58:12.130 align:middle line:90%
t minus t prime.

00:58:12.130 --> 00:58:19.970 align:middle line:90%


00:58:19.970 --> 00:58:22.940 align:middle line:90%
So this is the object.

00:58:22.940 --> 00:58:26.480 align:middle line:90%


00:58:26.480 --> 00:58:30.650 align:middle line:84%
