01:01:28.020 --> 01:01:31.870 align:middle line:84%
it's a delta function,
but this one, it's not.

01:01:31.870 --> 01:01:36.000 align:middle line:84%
But you can nevertheless you
can calculate this integral

01:01:36.000 --> 01:01:36.500 align:middle line:90%
exactly.

01:01:36.500 --> 01:01:41.010 align:middle line:90%


01:01:41.010 --> 01:01:43.410 align:middle line:84%
And also just
based on the here--

01:01:43.410 --> 01:01:46.093 align:middle line:84%
based on the
