01:05:45.440 --> 01:05:49.150 align:middle line:90%


01:05:49.150 --> 01:05:51.460 align:middle line:84%
So this a sense-- this is
approximately localized

01:05:51.460 --> 01:05:55.030 align:middle line:84%
